Shared grazing boundaries
Dependency failure must be declared ex ante, not discovered post hoc.
5. Fiscal Oracle
Tracks:
Alignment Bonds
Access Bonds
Obligation Pool balances
Function
Ensures:
Obligation can be settled.
Exposure symmetry remains intact.
No ecological gate is influenced by financial flow.
